Announcement
The
Schedule/Contact Information/Requirements has been updated! (2013/05/08)
    
Course Description
  
This PhD forum will invite active scholars and researchers in the IS and related fields to share their research studies and/or their publications experiences, with the goal of exposing students to state-of-the-art research issues. Each talk will last for about 120 minutes, followed by a 10-minute discussion session.
    



